  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enable the Federation in Africa to review recent&#xC2;&#xA0;DM deployments in terms of their efficiency and effectiveness in order to identify areas for improvement, and to provide refresher&#xC2;&#xA0;DM &#xC2;&#xA0;training for national society staff across the region.&#xC2;&#xA0; The intended outcome is to strengthen the ability of the Federation and national societies to respond quickly and effectively to disasters by training a number of staff in a range of skills required so that they can be deployed at national level or within the region when disaster strikes.</narrative>
